### 2.4. Objectives

Collect 3 fragments of the Heart of Aethel.

Overcome challenges and puzzles.

Ultimately, reassemble the Heart to stabilize the sky islands.

### 2.5. Embedded Movie Aspect

Upon completing a major objective (e.g., collecting a fragment, reassembling the Heart), the script generates a short, descriptive narrative sequence, providing a sense of cinematic progression within the text-based game.

